    <section xml:id="docnumber_fb">
      <title>General > Generating and viewing a document number</title>

      <para>You can set a document number for documents created in eformsign. You can set to generate document number automatically for each template, and can select one of four document number formats. The document number can be entered within the document using the document component. You can also see a separate column in the document list and search documents by the document number.</para>

      <para><emphasis role="bold">Generating a document number<indexterm class="singular">
          <primary>Template</primary>

          <secondary>Generate a document number</secondary>
        </indexterm></emphasis></para>

      <note>
        <para>Only the <emphasis role="bold">company administrator </emphasis> or <emphasis
        role="bold">Template manager</emphasis> can perform this action.</para>
      </note>

      <figure>
        <title>Setting document number</title>

        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="resources/template-setting-general-doc-numering1.png"
                       width="600"/>
          </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </figure>

      <orderedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>In the sidebar menu, click and go to the  <emphasis role="bold">Manage templates</emphasis>menu.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Click on the <emphasis role="bold">settings</emphasis>icon (<inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata contentwidth="33"
                           fileref="resources/config-icon.PNG"/>
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>) of the desired template <emphasis role="bold">to go to the Template settings</emphasis> page.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><emphasis role="bold">Tick the</emphasis>  <emphasis
          role="bold">Generate a document number</emphasis>checkbox in the General page.</para>

          <para><itemizedlist>
              <listitem>
                <para><emphasis role="bold">Selecting a document numbering rule</emphasis></para>
              </listitem>
            </itemizedlist><figure>
              <title>Select a document numbering rule</title>

              <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata contentwidth="400"
                             fileref="resources/template-setting-general-doc-numering1_1.png"/>
                </imageobject>
              </mediaobject>
            </figure><variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term><emphasis role="bold">▪ Serial number</emphasis></term>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Generated in the format of document creation order</para>

                  <para>E.g. 1, 2, 3...</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>

              <varlistentry>
                <term><emphasis role="bold">▪ Year_serial number</emphasis></term>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Generated in the format of document creation year + document creation order</para>

                  <para>E.g. 2020_1, 2020_2...</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist><variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term><emphasis role="bold">▪ Template_serial number</emphasis></term>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Generated in the format of template abbreviation + document creation order</para>

                  <para>E.g. Application 1, Application 2...</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>

              <varlistentry>
                <term><emphasis role="bold">▪ Template_year_serial number</emphasis></term>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Generated in the format of template abbreviation + document creation year + document creation order</para>

                  <para>E.g. Application 2020_1, Application 2020_2...</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist><itemizedlist>
              <listitem>
                <para><emphasis role="bold">Choosing when to numbered a document</emphasis></para>
              </listitem>
            </itemizedlist><variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>▪ <emphasis role="bold">Start</emphasis></term>

                <listitem>
                  <para>A number is generated when a document is start being created.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>

              <varlistentry>
                <term>▪ <emphasis role="bold">Complete</emphasis></term>

                <listitem>
                  <para>A document number is generated when a document has been completed after going through all the steps in the workflow.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Click the  <emphasis role="bold">Save</emphasis> button at the top right corner of the page to apply your changes.</para>
        </listitem>
      </orderedlist>

      <para><emphasis role="bold">Viewing a document number</emphasis></para>

      <para>A document number can be viewed on a document itself by using the document component and can also be viewed in the document list.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para><emphasis role="bold">Viewing a document number on the document itself</emphasis></para>

          <para>You can generate a document number on the document itself by using the document component in Form builder. <emphasis role="bold"></emphasis></para>

          <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>Open a file in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Add the document component in the desired location where the document number will be placed.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para><emphasis role="bold">Click the Upload button to upload the file to eformsign.</emphasis> </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para><emphasis role="bold">In Template settings > General,</emphasis><emphasis role="bold">tick the Generate a document number</emphasis>checkbox.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Select a document number rule.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para><emphasis role="bold">Click the Save</emphasis> button to save the settings.</para>
            </listitem>
          </orderedlist>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><emphasis role="bold">Viewing a document number in the document list</emphasis></para>

          <figure>
            <title>All documents - Document list</title>

            <mediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="resources/doc-list-docnumber1.PNG"
                           width="700"/>
              </imageobject>
            </mediaobject>
          </figure>

          <figure>
            <title>All documents - Document list - Document number</title>

            <mediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="resources/doc-list-docnumber2.png"
                           width="700"/>
              </imageobject>
            </mediaobject>
          </figure>

          <para>A document number can be viewed in the All documents menu (All documents, In progress, Action required, and Completed) and the Manage documents menu (requires document management permission).</para>

          <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>In the sidebar menu, click and go to the <emphasis role="bold">Documents</emphasis>or<emphasis role="bold">Manage documents</emphasis> menu.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Click the  <emphasis role="bold">column settings</emphasis> icon at the top right corner of the page.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Check <emphasis role="bold">Document number</emphasis>in the column list.</para>

              <para><inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                    <imagedata contentwidth="147"
                               fileref="resources/columnlist-docnum.png"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject></para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Check that <emphasis role="bold">the document number</emphasis> column is added.</para>
            </listitem>
          </orderedlist>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><emphasis role="bold">Searching for a document using a document number</emphasis></para>

          <para><inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="resources/doc-number-search.png"
                           width="600"/>
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject></para>

          <para>You can search a document by its document number via advanced search.</para>

          <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para><emphasis role="bold">Go to the Documents</emphasis> or <emphasis
              role="bold">Manage documents</emphasis> menu.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">the Advanced</emphasis> button on the top of the document list.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Select <emphasis role="bold">Document number</emphasis>among the search condition.</para>
            </listitem>

