    <section>
      <title>Set permissions</title>

      <para>You can set the permissions for the template usage and document management.</para>

      <figure>
        <title>Template settings > Set permissions</title>

        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="resources/template-setting-auth-new.PNG"
                       width="700"/>
          </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </figure>

      <para><emphasis role="bold">Template usage</emphasis></para>

      <para><indexterm class="singular">
          <primary>Template usage</primary>
        </indexterm>This permission is to create documents using the template, and you can select
      <emphasis role="bold">Allow all</emphasis> or <emphasis role="bold">Group or member</emphasis>to allow all the members or some members in the company to create documents using the template.Group or member</para>

      <para><emphasis role="bold">Document management</emphasis></para>

      <para><indexterm class="singular">
          <primary>Document management</primary>
        </indexterm>You can select groups or members to open documents created using the template, void completed documents, or remove documents permanently and these permissions can be set all or individually.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Open all documents (default): It is a default permission granted to a document manager regardless of selection, and it gives a permission to open all documents to the authorized groups or members.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Void completed documents (when selecting): Document management permission to approve voiding completed documents upon request of the document creator.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Remove documents (when selecting): Permission to permanently remove the document from the system</para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="resources/template-setting-auth-doc-new.PNG"
                     width="700"/>
        </imageobject>
      </mediaobject>
    </section>

