      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para><emphasis role="bold">Properties</emphasis>are to configure details of each step which are required including the step name.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><emphasis role="bold">In the Manage items tap,</emphasis>you can set fields to <emphasis role="bold">Allow access</emphasis>which allows recipient of the step to edit the fields, and<emphasis role="bold">Required field</emphasis> to make recipient to fill in the fields.</para>

