              </listitem>

              <listitem>
                <para><emphasis role="bold">Create documents from URL</emphasis> : When requesting to an external user who are not a member, create a public link for external recipients that they can access directly via the URL and view the document without signing in to the eformsign service.</para>
              </listitem>

              <listitem>
                <para><emphasis role="bold">Do not allow duplicate documents</emphasis> : Prevents sending duplicate documents, and selects a field that determines whether a document is duplicated or not.</para>
